  Why This Recipe Was Created:
This easy French macaron recipe makes a batch of the most dainty, delicate, and delicious cookies that will float right into your mouth and disappear. 
I've packed all my tips into this post to help you out!These French macarons make a very special treat to give your friends and family. They also 
look pretty on a plate for guests to indulge in when they come over.They can definitely be finicky but once you learn how to make 
macarons you’ll be hooked! Even if your cookies come out of the oven 
looking totally wrong they’ll still be delicious if not picture perfect.

